    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Oh, okey then Sure! That's the spirit [tn]"
            ],
            [
                "It's not so far from here. We can even walk it."
            ],
            [
                "As we walk around the block a silence grows until it can't be ignored anymore."
            ],
            [
                "So, uh... You like music?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, I guess I do as many people do in this world."
            ],
            [
                "Dumb question. I know, but... is one of those ice breakers."
            ],
            [
                "Like at the start of every school year?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, I always found them dumb."
            ],
            [
                "Of course all of us will like music, or watch tv, or play videogames."
            ],
            [
                "It's a pretty easy answer to give to strangers."
            ],
            [
                "It's not like we would give any deep dark secret to people we meet on the first day."
            ],
            [
                "That's not even important. You can just see it all regardless."
            ],
            [
                "What do you mean? how?"
            ],
            [
                "Oh, uh... Uhm..."
            ],
            [
                "The faces, yeah, in the eyes and stuff. Easy to read."
            ],
            [
                "Oh, Anyways we're here."
            ],
            [
                "The apartment complex is slightly worn down, it seems we have to go some two or three floors up."
            ],
            [
                "Victor's apartment is messy, with clothes in the ground and some music sheets sprinkled."
            ],
            [
                "As we both enter the room, Victor quickly reaches por [his] computer and turns it off and opens the room's curtains to bring light."
            ],
            [
                "So, we're here!"
            ],
            [
                "It's... uh... a little messy."
            ],
            [
                "But that's how creatives work around y'know. It's messy but I know where it all is."
            ],
            [
                "There is silence that begins to grow akward despite being only for a second."
            ],
            [
                "So... where is your... uh, instrument?"
            ],
            [
                "Right, here yeah."
            ],
            [
                "Victor pulls up an acustic guitar and sits on the bed while [he] prepares the pick."
            ],
            [
                "Alright, uh.. this one 's new... been practicing a little, so... expect maybe some errors."
            ],
            [
                "Victor coughs a little while adjusting the guitar and takes a moment to prepare the first pluck of strings"
            ],
            [
                "......."
            ],
            [
                "♪ Wake up, Alone ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ It's 3 am  ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ With no one at my siiiidee. ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ My sweetheart ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ Where are youuu? ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ I need someone... ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ To give ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ And share ♪"
            ],
            [
                "♪ all my looooveeee.. ♪"
            ],
            [
                "Victor continues to play the guitar."
            ],
            [
                "..... That's all the lyrics I practiced."
            ],
            [
                "What uh, whadaya think?"
            ],
            [
                "Woah, i'd say.... you're good."
            ],
            [
                "How long have you been playing?"
            ],
            [
                "Huh... You know... I have no idea."
            ],
            [
                "Uh, do... do you liked it?"
            ],
            [
                "I have been practicing this song since.."
            ],
            [
                "Since I saw you at the coffee."
            ],
            [
                "The air slightly flows through the window. As we both stay quiet."
            ],
            [
                "We barely see each other eyes, but im sure we give a glance to each other."
            ],
            [
                "The air is starting to feel warmer."
            ],
            [
                "So... uhmm-- So.. you... like-"
            ],
            [
                "My phone buzzes and a school notification enters"
            ],
            [
                "Oh sorry, my... um. I got to go now."
            ],
            [
                "Wait so soon?"
            ],
            [
                "I gotta go do homework sorry."
            ],
            [
                "But... But, I will see you later right?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, we can see each other, I gotta go, bye."
            ],
            [
                "I try to hide my face as I walk my way outside."
            ],
            [
                ""
            ]
